Welcome back WakeDevils! We hope you had a Merry Christmas and Happy New Year! This winter break we were invited by @outsidelifetravel to snowboard for a week in Park City, Utah. Although wakeboarding comes first, we always love the opportunity to get out on the mountains and rip🏂  #utah #parkcity #snowboarding #wakedevils

Our first #wipeoutwednesday of the year was HEAVY featuring @veji.8 

#skeezer #slam #wakedevils #wakeboarding #stillwonthechallenge #betterthancam #wipeout #ronix #action #heneedsomemilk

If y’all didn’t know, our guy @brycehen_az is always pushing our riders to get out of their comfort zone. One of his favorite tricks to teach is back 1s. This year @todd_balvin and @enzovidigal have been putting the work in and dropping some bangers!!!

#wakeboarding #wakedevils #backone #blind #brazil #ronix #actionwatersports #brycemademedoit #g23

#wipeoutwednesday #wakedevils #360 #spinning #crash #fail

Cactus Classic 2023 🌵

We want to give a big thank you to all of the teams for coming out and competing and all the family and friends for coming out and supporting. It was a blast having all of y’all out here and getting to give y’all a little taste of Arizona. We can’t wait to send it out to all of your comps these coming months!!!

Shoutout to our sponsors for allowing us to put this competition on. We wouldn’t be able to do it all without @ronixwakeboards @maneraamerica @donjoyperformance @awsboats 

Special shoutout to our guy @brycehen_az for getting all of our riders ready to compete and coming in clutch and pulling some of the comp!!!
